Package hr.fer.oop.lab3

Class Team

  • java.lang.Object
    • hr.fer.oop.lab3.Team
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ManageableTeam
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClubTeam, NationalTeam
    public abstract class Team
extends Object
implements ManageableTeam
    This class represents a football team, along with its name and formation. It implements a collection containing registered players and starting eleven players of type FootballPlayer. This class is used as a base class for its subclasses.
    Author:
    Matija
